OL,4,CCovid: New Wales curriculum 'must be
OL,5,Cdelayed' to aid pupils
OL,6, Rollout of a new school curriculum in
OL,7, Wales must be delayed so teachers can
OL,8, focus on helping pupils in the wake of
OL,9, the pandemic, a union has warned.
OL,11,FChanges are set to be introduced in
OL,12,F2022 for all children currently in year
OL,13,Fthree or below.
OL,15,FHowever, the NASUWT said it must be
OL,16,Fpushed back to enable teachers to help
OL,17,Fpupils get back on track, otherwise the
OL,18,Fcurriculum's success will be at risk.
OL,20,FThe Welsh government said curriculum
OL,21,Freform remained a "priority".
